{"tid":1385725,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」其實各銀行用戶聯署呼籲銀行保障罷工員工有無可行性？","createTime":"2019-07-30T06:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:02:19.000Z","uid":34279,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"31f743ca7cc21028ec8294f3ba42eede03ef04ab","tid":1385725,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"8月5日全員罷工<br />\n其實員工對罷工最大恐懼不外乎被公司秋後算帳，而銀行或者其他機構因爲在支共有相關業務而不會正面支持或回應罷工。<br />\n<br />\n如果各大銀行用戶聯署要求銀行保障當日罷工員工不會被秋後算帳 ；用戶願意承擔當日罷工的個人損失之類，會不會增長各銀行員工罷工的機會？<br />\n <br />\n而員工自行罷工責任不在銀行，銀行無需正面表態。<br />\n<br />\n聯署時用戶就附上該銀行的提款卡或信用卡作證，Etc.<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲有無咩意見或者想法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港人不如勇敢一次，爭返一口氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d02841decd94dd515dafa776da242a98ec730d2","tid":1385725,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:59:18.000Z","msg":"另外聯署的話 上一代支持抗爭而又無從下手的大眾都可以輕鬆參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3108b6f2339b18d55355b26ad533a8347755b3","tid":1385725,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T06:59:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20195072a3674c4bf0531773561f5856b6b04451","tid":1385725,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1d6857212a5a49d2096df949618fe6ea68aee9a","tid":1385725,"uid":164938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T07:00:41.000Z","msg":"Fact checked<br />\n明天機場博覽館要人！！<br />\n7.31<br />\n16:00-17:30<br />\n機場Asia World Expo-Summit 2號展館<br />\n政府開pre policy address meeting! <br />\n會議是為運輸及貿易界而設既諮詢會，將有好多公司出席！<br />\n<br />\n聽日7.31機場博覽館要人！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385635\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385635</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e41de9fd35c1301af1eafd83051c818d7d02d883","tid":1385725,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited